Officer Michael Slager, 33, is being kept in isolation for fear prisoners will try to kill him .
On Tuesday, his wife Jamie, who is eight-and-a-half months pregnant, was allowed to speak to him for the first time since he was charged with murder in North Charleston, South Carolina, on Tuesday .
Slager, a North Charleston police veteran, is charged with murdering Walter Scott, 50, after he stopped him over a broken tail light on Saturday .
His attorney says Slager is housed in a room with one window and does not interact with other detainees .